{"tid":745623,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"如何煉成香港人嘅奴性","createTime":"2018-07-17T02:52:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-17T13:20:00.000Z","uid":151717,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ade2e8b1265bee2d5fc060b3a5130da75b33d35a","tid":745623,"uid":151717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T02:52:30.000Z","msg":"肯定由細做起，由小學個啲濕鳩camp開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n個陣我好彩去唔到，啲同學去完翻黎個撚個都變到好似中共士兵咁，上堂做個啲濕鳩敬禮好撚似士兵大大聲嗌。我個下係呆咗，我變到好似異類咁，得我一個好普通講good morning Miss Chan<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後淨翻個半年成班同學都係咁敬禮，我就直程放棄唔出聲算，反正佢地嗌得咁大聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n除咗小學之外，中學都係一樣有呢啲camp。雖然我都係因為要比賽去唔到，不過聽翻啲同學講個camp好on9，入面啲濕鳩camp導師當正自己係大佬咁，唔撚理啲學生嘅尊嚴，迫你體力勞動、當住咁多人屌鳩你，話你廢、唔俾你食飯之類<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  諗返都覺得自己好彩去唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有幾個camp係用黎馴服啲香港人，唔知大家又知唔知邊幾個呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一齊討論下"},{"pid":"a9c9e42addc27ec879e366e63cae930e11270821","tid":745623,"uid":85564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T05:30:40.000Z","msg":"indeed"},{"pid":"fb4138a0f822df9a8bf7b4a2e8133b331a4a4f40","tid":745623,"uid":75095,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T05:34:45.000Z","msg":"未去過呢啲camp<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3018e6224f3cd3fc4323dbcfbfbf1f30caaed410","tid":745623,"uid":151717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb4138a0f822df9a8bf7b4a2e8133b331a4a4f40","tid":745623,"uid":75095,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T05:34:45.000Z","msg":"未去過呢啲camp<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T05:36:36.000Z","msg":"我阿哥小學個陣俾學校迫去黃埔軍校<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲要著住嗰啲on9制服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好撚慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7ec121989fb025a6b763350ca920d8099c46442","tid":745623,"uid":80598,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T05:45:17.000Z","msg":"聽過啲乜鳩領袖營，自己冇玩，但有Frd被迫參加<br />\n佢話，通常一入到去佢地就會不斷踩你，踩到你一文不值<br />\n然後就開始建立你嘅自信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但班人係好鐘意聽話嘅人（狗），同時會玩鳩啲唔聽話嘅人<br />\n結果成班同學仔就喺度奉承班人，又聽聽話話噉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我Frd話成班人（連埋班同學）都痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢自己全程冇理班人，Hea玩"},{"pid":"3377a250b1f0136336103163859768d760bf77c3","tid":745623,"uid":62471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T06:17:07.000Z","msg":"中學小學去啲camp全部勁好彩<br />\n純玩"},{"pid":"1a3cc06d2a40324d9ee8c4a2b4729468aa691f88","tid":745623,"uid":151717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T11:16:11.000Z","msg":"近排又有一個中共勞改營，成班中學生俾人撚狗撚到變咗瀨共狗啦，入呢個營嘅全部男仔好似都要剪平頭定光頭，然後又要步操又盛咁，真係入去唔知為咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8e00442cab78bdac7ed47438776ad15af57e585","tid":745623,"uid":108006,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T13:20:00.000Z","msg":"紅底中學逼人去大陸軍訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n要步操，唱支那軍歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲播片介紹支那軍隊好勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，嗰時攰到仆街喺度洽眼瞓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n保良局嗰啲camp<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n逼人大聲叫口號，有同學真係好投入，第二日把聲沙哂<br />\n其中一晚要我哋圍埋反省，播搧情音樂，有人咗出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}